{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":656,"text":"When I was a young officer, they told me"},{"time":2626,"text":"to follow my instincts,"},{"time":4894,"text":"to go with my gut,"},{"time":7150,"text":"and what I've learned"},{"time":9160,"text":"is that often our instincts are wrong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13544,"text":"In the summer of 2010,"},{"time":16720,"text":"there was a massive leak of classified documents"},{"time":20059,"text":"that came out of the Pentagon."},{"time":23032,"text":"It shocked the world,"},{"time":24848,"text":"it shook up the American government,"},{"time":26423,"text":"and it made people ask a lot of questions,"},{"time":28576,"text":"because the sheer amount of information"},{"time":31257,"text":"that was let out, and the potential impacts,"},{"time":34832,"text":"were significant."},{"time":37408,"text":"And one of the first questions we asked ourselves"},{"time":41430,"text":"was why would a young soldier have access"},{"time":44148,"text":"to that much information?"},{"time":47080,"text":"Why would we let sensitive things"},{"time":49606,"text":"be with a relatively young person?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":53764,"text":"In the summer of 2003, I was assigned to command"},{"time":56886,"text":"a special operations task force,"},{"time":59390,"text":"and that task force was spread across the Mideast"},{"time":61530,"text":"to fight al Qaeda."},{"time":63118,"text":"Our main effort was inside Iraq,"},{"time":66115,"text":"and our specified mission"},{"time":68082,"text":"was to defeat al Qaeda in Iraq."},{"time":69936,"text":"For almost five years I stayed there,"},{"time":73040,"text":"and we focused on fighting a war"},{"time":74850,"text":"that was unconventional and it was difficult"},{"time":79896,"text":"and it was bloody"},{"time":81736,"text":"and it often claimed its highest price"},{"time":84830,"text":"among innocent people."},{"time":87904,"text":"We did everything we could"},{"time":90409,"text":"to stop al Qaeda"},{"time":92318,"text":"and the foreign fighters that\ncame in as suicide bombers"},{"time":95603,"text":"and as accelerants to the violence."},{"time":100718,"text":"We honed our combat skills,"},{"time":102740,"text":"we developed new equipment,"},{"time":105576,"text":"we parachuted, we helicoptered,"},{"time":108030,"text":"we took small boats, we drove, and we walked"},{"time":110488,"text":"to objectives night after night to stop"},{"time":113498,"text":"the killing that this network was putting forward."},{"time":118850,"text":"We bled,"},{"time":121390,"text":"we died,"},{"time":122879,"text":"and we killed to stop that organization"},{"time":127730,"text":"from the violence that they were putting"},{"time":129473,"text":"largely against the Iraqi people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133702,"text":"Now, we did what we knew,"},{"time":136280,"text":"how we had grown up, and\none of the things that we knew,"},{"time":139194,"text":"that was in our DNA, was secrecy."},{"time":142320,"text":"It was security. It was protecting information."},{"time":144237,"text":"It was the idea that information was the lifeblood"},{"time":147050,"text":"and it was what would protect and keep people safe."},{"time":150690,"text":"And we had a sense that,"},{"time":152585,"text":"as we operated within our organizations,"},{"time":154596,"text":"it was important to keep information"},{"time":156514,"text":"in the silos within the organizations,"},{"time":158825,"text":"particularly only give information"},{"time":161739,"text":"to people had a demonstrated need to know."},{"time":165931,"text":"But the question often came, who needed to know?"},{"time":170570,"text":"Who needed, who had to have the information"},{"time":173933,"text":"so that they could do the important \nparts of the job that you needed?"},{"time":177004,"text":"And in a tightly coupled world,"},{"time":179056,"text":"that's very hard to predict."},{"time":181854,"text":"It's very hard to know who needs to have information"},{"time":184798,"text":"and who doesn't."},{"time":186305,"text":"I used to deal with intelligence agencies,"},{"time":188284,"text":"and I'd complain that they weren't\nsharing enough intelligence,"},{"time":190451,"text":"and with a straight face, they'd\nlook at me and they'd say,"},{"time":192841,"text":"\"What aren't you getting?\" (Laughter)"},{"time":194988,"text":"I said, \"If I knew that, we wouldn't have a problem.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":200470,"text":"But what we found is we had to change."},{"time":202072,"text":"We had to change our culture about information."},{"time":204249,"text":"We had to knock down walls. We had to share."},{"time":206366,"text":"We had to change from who needs to know"},{"time":209434,"text":"to the fact that who doesn't know,"},{"time":211557,"text":"and we need to tell, and tell\nthem as quickly as we can."},{"time":214791,"text":"It was a significant culture shift for an organization"},{"time":217917,"text":"that had secrecy in its DNA."}]},{"cues":[{"time":223241,"text":"We started by doing things, by building,"},{"time":225517,"text":"not working in offices,"},{"time":227222,"text":"knocking down walls, working in things we called"},{"time":228887,"text":"situation awareness rooms,"},{"time":231345,"text":"and in the summer of 2007,"},{"time":233821,"text":"something happened which demonstrated this."},{"time":235444,"text":"We captured the personnel records"},{"time":237636,"text":"for the people who were bringing foreign fighters"},{"time":239836,"text":"into Iraq."},{"time":241991,"text":"And when we got the personnel records, typically,"},{"time":243839,"text":"we would have hidden these,"},{"time":245153,"text":"shared them with a few intelligence agencies,"},{"time":247491,"text":"and then try to operate with them."},{"time":249287,"text":"But as I was talking to my intelligence officer,"},{"time":251325,"text":"I said, \"What do we do?\""},{"time":252175,"text":"And he said, \"Well, you found them.\" Our command."},{"time":255201,"text":"\"You can just declassify them.\""},{"time":257565,"text":"And I said, \"Well, can we declassify them?"},{"time":259213,"text":"What if the enemy finds out?\""},{"time":260223,"text":"And he says, \"They're their personnel records.\""},{"time":262835,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":264235,"text":"So we did,"},{"time":265317,"text":"and a lot of people got upset about that,"},{"time":267351,"text":"but as we passed that information around,"},{"time":269835,"text":"suddenly you find that information is only of value"},{"time":272725,"text":"if you give it to people who have the ability"},{"time":274581,"text":"to do something with it."},{"time":276719,"text":"The fact that I know something has zero value"},{"time":278845,"text":"if I'm not the person who can actually"},{"time":280333,"text":"make something better because of it."},{"time":282207,"text":"So as a consequence, what we did was"},{"time":284083,"text":"we changed the idea of information,"},{"time":287193,"text":"instead of knowledge is power,"},{"time":289477,"text":"to one where sharing is power."},{"time":292423,"text":"It was the fundamental shift,"},{"time":294395,"text":"not new tactics, not new weapons,"},{"time":296733,"text":"not new anything else."},{"time":298037,"text":"It was the idea that we were now part of a team"},{"time":300815,"text":"in which information became the essential link"},{"time":303163,"text":"between us, not a block between us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307661,"text":"And I want everybody to take a deep breath"},{"time":310243,"text":"and let it out,"},{"time":312365,"text":"because in your life, there's going to be information"},{"time":314299,"text":"that leaks out you're not going to like."},{"time":316631,"text":"Somebody's going to get my college grades out,"},{"time":318877,"text":"a that's going to be a disaster. (Laughter)"},{"time":322904,"text":"But it's going to be okay, and I will tell you that"},{"time":326273,"text":"I am more scared of the bureaucrat"},{"time":329493,"text":"that holds information in a desk drawer"},{"time":331945,"text":"or in a safe than I am of someone who leaks,"},{"time":334741,"text":"because ultimately, we'll be better off if we share."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337677,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339437,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":345761,"text":"Helen Walters: So I don't know if\nyou were here this morning,"},{"time":347337,"text":"if you were able to catch Rick Ledgett,"},{"time":349637,"text":"the deputy director of the NSA"},{"time":351469,"text":"who was responding to Edward\nSnowden's talk earlier this week."},{"time":355133,"text":"I just wonder, do you think the American government"},{"time":357445,"text":"should give Edward Snowden amnesty?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":360133,"text":"Stanley McChrystal: I think that\nRick said something very important."},{"time":362581,"text":"We, most people, don't know all the facts."},{"time":365201,"text":"I think there are two parts of this."},{"time":366553,"text":"Edward Snowden shined a\nlight on an important need"},{"time":370293,"text":"that people had to understand."},{"time":371783,"text":"He also took a lot of documents that he didn't have"},{"time":374765,"text":"the knowledge to know the importance of,"},{"time":377357,"text":"so I think we need to learn the facts about this case"},{"time":379790,"text":"before we make snap judgments"},{"time":381337,"text":"about Edward Snowden."},{"time":383485,"text":"HW: Thank you so much. Thank you."},{"time":385669,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}